product_name: LifeProof Life Jacket Float Case - iPhone 5
long_description: The LifeProof Life Jacket float case adds flotation to your Apple iPhone 5 when used with a LifeProof case (sold separately). Life Jacket float case fits seamlessly over the LifeProof case to prevent your iPhone from sinking into the depths on your next aquatic adventure.
